<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MyMood Journal - Kelompok 3</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quicksand:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --wood-brown: #8d5524;
            --soft-yellow: #fdf5e6;
            --green-btn: #4caf50;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
            background: #fdf5e6 url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cream-paper.png');
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        /* Header Gaya Kayu */
        .header {
            background: #a67c52;
            background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/wood-pattern.png');
            padding: 15px;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #5d4037;
        }

        .header h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.2rem; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .total-points { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 0.9rem; }

        /* Main Content */
        .content { padding: 25px; text-align: center; }
        h3 { color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .sub-text { color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }

        /* Mood Buttons */
        .mood-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .mood-item {
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 10px 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            background: white;
        }

        .mood-item:hover { border-color: #a67c52; background: #fffde7; }
        .mood-item div { font-size: 1.5rem; }
        .mood-item span { font-size: 0.75rem; display: block; margin-top: 5px; }

        /* Form Input */
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 2px dashed #bdc3c7;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: inherit;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: #fcfcfc;
        }

        .btn-save {
            background: #4caf50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px #2e7d32;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-save:active { transform: translateY(4px); box-shadow: none; }

        /* Level Bar */
        .level-section { margin-top: 25px; text-align: left; }
        .progress-container {
            background: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            height: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .progress-bar {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #3498db, #2980b9);
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .footer-note { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #bdc3c7; margin-top: 30px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>MYMOOD JOURNAL üçÉ</h2>
            <div class="total-points">üèÜ TOTAL: 120 POINTS</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h3>Bagaimana Perasaanmu?</h3>
            <p class="sub-text">( Pilih satu untuk dapat +10 Poin! )</p>

            <div class="mood-grid">
                <div class="mood-item"><div>üòä</div><span>Joy</span></div>
                <div class="mood-item"><div>üò¢</div><span>Sad</span></div>
                <div class="mood-item"><div>üò°</div><span>Anger</span></div>
                <div class="mood-item"><div>üò®</div><span>Fear</span></div>
                <div class="mood-item"><div>ü§¢</div><span>Disgust</span></div>
            </div>

            <textarea placeholder="Tulis alasan singkat..." rows="3"></textarea>

            <button class="btn-save">SIMPAN JURNAL</button>

            <div class="level-section">
                <strong>LEVEL SAAT INI:</strong>
                <div class="progress-container">
                    <div class="progress-bar"></div>
                </div>
                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 5px;">50% Menuju Level Berikutnya</p>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-note">
                Akses via Port 1912 (Nginx Reverse Proxy)
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
